OL,3,CFarmers say inheritance tax changes
OL,4,Cwill create 'massive' problems for
OL,5,Cindustry
OL,7,FFarmers in Cumbria and southern
OL,8,FScotland say inheritance tax changes
OL,9,Ffor agricultural families will create
OL,10,F"massive implications" for the future
OL,11,Fof the industry.
OL,13,FThousands of people including members
OL,14,Fof the National Farmers' Union have
OL,15,Fgathered outside Parliament to protest
OL,16,Fagainst the introduction of farming
OL,17,Finheritance tax.
OL,19,FA 20% rate was announced by the
OL,20,FChancellor Rachel Reeves in last
OL,21,Fmonth's budget.
