OL,3,CFarmers say inheritance tax changes
OL,4,Cwill create 'massive' problems for
OL,5,Cindustry
OL,7,FThe tax announcement - set to come in
OL,8,Ffrom April 2026 - will apply to
OL,9,Fcombined agricultural and business
OL,10,Fproperty worth more than #1m.
OL,12,FAn inheritance tax rate of 40% is the
OL,13,Fstandard rate applied to other land
OL,14,Fand properties.
OL,16,FJohn Longmire, an Ulverston farmer and
OL,17,FChair of Cumbria NFU, says the policy
OL,18,Fwill 'hurt' families across the UK.
