OL,3,CFarmers say inheritance tax changes
OL,4,Cwill create 'massive' problems for
OL,5,Cindustry
OL,7,FHe said: "These proposed changes
OL,8,Fannounced in the budget will create
OL,9,Fmassive implications for family farms.
OL,10,FIt hurts when they turn round and say
OL,11,Fthey've done this so it does not
OL,12,Faffect family farming - it's totally
OL,13,Funtrue.
OL,15,F"There was no consultation on the
OL,16,Feffect this would have on family farms
OL,17,Fand ultimately, they said they would
OL,18,Fnot touch it not long before the
OL,19,Fbudget."
