OL,4,Cwill create 'massive' problems for
OL,5,Cindustry
OL,7,FPeter Douglas, a farmer from Jedburgh,
OL,8,Fin the Scottish Borders, says he
OL,9,Fdecided to join the rally in London
OL,10,Fbecause he feels "this is one of the
OL,11,Ffinal straws" for farming.
OL,13,FHe said: "We've all come down because
OL,14,Fthey brought this policy out of the
OL,15,Fblue, it was not in the manifesto -
OL,16,Fthey have not got a mandate for doing
OL,17,Fit.
