OL,3,CFarmers say inheritance tax changes
OL,4,Cwill create 'massive' problems for
OL,5,Cindustry
OL,7,F"We provide food, we provide
OL,8,Flandscape... and we feel like the rugs
OL,9,Fhave been pulled off from under our
OL,10,Ffeet. It feels very emotional, there
OL,11,Fseems a real togetherness about
OL,12,Fsomething that we can all get behind.
OL,13,FIt's not just the sheep farmers, it's
OL,14,Fnot the poultry farmers - it's our way
OL,15,Fof life.
OL,17,F"I think this could turn out to be a
OL,18,Fmomentum changer for the countryside,"
OL,19,FPeter added.
