OL,7,FEnvironment Secretary Steve Reed -
OL,8,Fappearing before a parliamentary
OL,9,Fcommittee - says he rejects farmer's
OL,10,Fclaims that some assets worth less
OL,11,Fthan #1m will be affected.
OL,13,FIn an interview with ITV News, he
OL,14,Fsaid: "It's only right that we've had
OL,15,Fto ask the wealthiest landowners and
OL,16,Fthe biggest farms to pay their fair
OL,17,Fshare. I would emphasis only 500 farms
OL,18,Fwill be affected, the vast majority of
OL,19,Ffarmers will pay no more under the new
OL,20,Fscheme as they do under the current
OL,21,Fone.
